# Derived ledger aggregates (Protocol 0.5) — pure functions of state/ledger/*.json
# (+ state/campaign.json), regenerated by scripts/regenerate_state.py (`make ledger`).
# Never committed; the records under state/ledger/ are the source of truth.
state/experiment_ledger.jsonl
state/research_tree.json
state/val_exposure.json
state/INDEX.md

# Crash-safety: regenerate_state.py writes derived files via mkstemp(prefix=".tmp-")
# in state/ before os.replace. A crash mid-write can leave one behind; never commit it.
state/.tmp-*
.tmp-*
